        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Crisis Counseling Act </b></p> <p>This bill provides for immediate approval of any request by a state, local, or tribal government for crisis counseling and training after the President declares a major disaster under the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act. </p>]]>
        </text>
